OL,8,     Gand technology already one and
OL,9,     Gthe same - accelerating towards
OL,10,     Gan inevitable climax?
OL,11,G0055FBlind Eye Artist
OL,12,     GThe origin story of renowned
OL,13,     GAmerican painter Justin
OL,14,     GWadlington, known as the Blind
OL,15,     GEye Artist, who rose from the
OL,16,     Gstreets of Philadelphia with no
OL,17,     Gformal art training.
